epler]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|49\n| Actress and presenter (''[[General Hospital]]'', [[Home Shopping Network|HSN]] host)\n|-\n|February 4\n|[[Augusta Dabney]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|89\n| Actress (''[[Another World (TV series)|Another World]]'', ''[[A World Apart (TV series)|A World Apart]]'', ''[[Loving (TV series)|Loving]]'')\n|-\n|February 6\n|[[John McWethy]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|60\n| [[ABC News]] correspondent from 1979 to 2006\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|February 10\n|[[Ron Leavitt]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|60\n| Writer and producer (''[[Happy Days]]'', ''[[Married... with Children]]'')\n|-\n|[[Roy Scheider]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|75\n| Actor (Capt. Bridger on ''[[seaQuest]]'')\n|-\n|[[Steve Gerber]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|60\n| Illustrator/animator (''[[Thundarr The Barbarian]]'')\n|-\n|February 12\n|[[David Groh]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|68\n| Actor (Joe Gerard on ''[[Rhoda]]'')\n|-\n|February 14\n|[[Perry Lopez]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|78\n| Character actor (''[[Star Trek]]'')\n|-\n|February 18\n|[[Grits Gresham]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|85\n| Outdoor sportscaster (''[[The American Sportsman]]'')\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|February 27\n|[[Myron Cope]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|79\n| Sportscaster at [[WPGP (AM)|WTAE]]/[[Pittsburgh]] and color commentator for [[Pittsburgh Steelers]] broadcasts\n|-\n|[[William F. Buckley, Jr.]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|82\n| Host and commentator (''[[Firing Line (TV series)|Firing Line]]'')\n|-\n|March 16\n|[[Ivan Dixon]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|76\n| Actor, producer and director (''[[Hogan's Heroes]]'')\n|-\n|April 5\n|[[Charlton Heston]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|84\n| Actor (''[[The Colbys]]'')\n|-\n|April 8\n|[[Stanley Kamel]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|65\n| Actor (''[[Monk (TV series)|Monk]]'')\n|-\n|May 1\n|[[Hager Twins]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|66\n| One-half of Hager Twins and a regular on ''[[Hee Haw]]''\n|-\n